 it isn’t exactly a matter of sculpture—à moins que tu ne confondes la galanterie avec la Galatée—which, however, is pardonable at your age. No, no—it’s all much less complicated. Only don’t be so bashful with me, I won’t bite you, I simply can’t stand lads qui se tiennent toujours sur leurs gardes. If you don’t have anything more interesting in view, we can return via Grenlog and dine on the lakeside, and then we’ll think up something.”

